TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT New_Salesforce_Case.LastModifiedDate as LastModifiedDate, 1 as dummy FROM $$TARGET_SCHEMA_DET_STG.New_Salesforce_Case WHERE LastModifiedDate IN (SELECT max(LastModifiedDate) FROM $$TARGET_SCHEMA_DET_STG.New_Salesforce_Case)
